00:42:46.080 --> 00:42:47.640
Aku akan melepaskan ayahmu.

00:42:52.920 --> 00:42:54.520
Saya bukan orang jahat!

00:42:55.680 --> 00:42:56.760
Tunggu sebentar.

00:42:58.720 --> 00:43:00.360
